'''1852年大西洋飓风季'''是有纪录以来第一个所有[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]都达到飓风强度的[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风季]]，截至[[2016年大西洋飓风季|2016年]]，这种情况一共只发生过三次<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 }}</ref>。全季经确认共形成五个热带气旋，第一个在八月中旬形成，最后一个于十月中旬消散，都在[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]每年绝大多数热带天气活动的时间范围内，不过本季没有任何两场风暴在同一时间共存，飓风学者迈克尔·切诺维斯认为其中两个气旋实际上是同一个<ref name="cheno">{{cite web | author = Michael Chenoweth | year = 2006 | title = A Reassessment of Historical Atlantic Basin Tropical Cyclone Activity, 1700–1855 | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | accessdate = 2008-05-25 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/HURDAT/Chenoweth/chenoweth06.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151105080711/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Chenoweth/chenoweth06.pdf | archivedate = 2015-11-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

本季可能还有其他未经确认的热带气旋形成，[[气象学|气象学家]][[克里斯托弗·朗诗|克里斯托弗·朗诗]]估计正式数据库中记载的每年风暴数量有可能比实际情况少六场，这主要是因为过去缺乏包括气象卫星在内的现代观测手段，部分热带气旋规模不大，同时船只观测记录不足，沿海地区居住的人口较少，部分风暴也没有直接对陆地构成显著影响<ref>{{cite web | author = Chris Landsea | year = 2007 | title = Counting Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Back to 1900 | publisher = American Meteorological Society | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/landsea-eos-may012007.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2007-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070714114214/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/landsea-eos-may012007.pdf }}</ref>。
